<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: auto;
        height: 100hv;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }
      header {
        background-color: #0279b1;
        height: 5rem;
        width: 100%;
      }
      main {
        background-color: aliceblue !important;
        text-align: justify;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
        <table style="width: 100%; height:100%;">
            <td style="text-align: center;">
                <img
                src="https://pacecode.com.np/image/assets/logo_w.png"
                style="height: 3rem; width: 5rem; "
              />
            </td>
        </table>
      
    </header>
    <main>
      <div style="padding: 1rem">
        <span style="font-weight: bolder; line-height: 24pt"
          >Dear, <%= fullName %></span
        >
        <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 16pt; margin-top: 2rem">
          Thank you for your application for the position of <strong><%= position %></strong>  at
          Pace Code Pvt. Ltd. 
          <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem" >
            We are a Software Company, we develop top-notch products for the
            consumers around the world. We are specialized in custom software
            development, mobile, and web application development, and UI/UX
            design. 
            
           <div style="margin-top:1.5rem">
            The further process for our recruitment requires a thorough
            screening of your CV. Therefore, we request you to be patient, if you
            advance to a further round we will contact you through the email you
            have provided or through a phone call. For any further inquiries you
            can contact us through this email.
           </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <div style="background-color: aliceblue">
        <div style="padding: 1rem">
          <div>Best Regards,</div>
          <div>Human Resource Team</div>
          <div>Pace Code Pvt. Ltd.</div>
          <div>Kathmandu Nepal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          background-color: #0279b1;
          height: 5rem;
          width: 100%;
          color: white;
        "
      >
        <div style="text-align: center; padding-top: 1.9rem">
          &#169; 2022 Pace Code
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
